resourceName)) {\n            assertThat(inputStream).isNotNull();\n            return inputStream.readAllBytes();\n        }\n    }\n}\n\nclass ExposedAntClassLoader2 extends AntClassLoader2 {\n    Class<?> defineClassFromBytes(byte[] classData, String className) throws IOException {\n        return defineClassFromData(null, classData, className);\n    }\n}\n\nclass AntClassLoader2Fixture {\n    // Loaded from copied bytecode by AntClassLoader2.\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1355, "output": 989, "cacheRead": 14848, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 17192, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777694129360, "responseId": "resp_0be572b0bcda8af70169f575b1b2a081939cf247275c604f43"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_NsmDroCmrtEe3b4vAeT4leC3|fc_0be572b0bcda8af70169f575b8b2e88193828b72e332289047", "toolName": "write", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Successfully wrote 2036 bytes to tests/src/ant/ant/1.6/src/test/java/ant/ant/AntClassLoader2Test.java"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777694139925}]}
