[thinking] I'm looking at a possible issue with the `definePackage(null,...)` call that leads to an NPE because it checks `container.isDirectory` when `container` is null. We need to provide a valid `File` temp directory path instead. It seems important that the `defineClassFromData` method also requires a container for the package. Without a directory, there's no manifest available, so I’ll focus on updating the subclass method to pass a proper `File` parameter while testing with temp directories.
