has anything to do with it. I'm pondering if line coverage isn’t hit because `definePackage` might return early.\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_sLpRr3TGphzwvffhFDqbi2R5|fc_0be572b0bcda8af70169f5766847688193b011885ff334460a", "name": "bash", "arguments": {"command": "grep -H \"timestamp\" tests/src/ant/ant/1.6/build/test-results/test/TEST-ant.ant.AntClassLoader*.xml", "timeout": 10}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 890, "output": 1292, "cacheRead": 37888, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 40070, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777694294076, "responseId": "resp_0be572b0bcda8af70169f576568b80819381fe18b8c09aa8fc"}}
